The evidence with the title 'Reject Broward penny-tax slush fund. Trust-us transportation plan is ... ' says Oct 13, 2018  ... Broward County over - reached by putting a penny sales tax increase for transportation on the november ballot. The tax would last 30 years and raise $16 billion . How the money would be spent is "flexible," meaning the plan isn't solid. The Sun Sentinel Editorial Board encourages voters to vote no . 
